$NetBSD: patch-aa,v 1.16 2011/03/10 23:38:42 pettai Exp $

Do not install by default Perl scripts; they are installed via
${INSTALL_SCRIPT} if the user set the "perl" option.

Do not remove the *.la files.

$NetBSD: patch-aa,v 1.16 2011/03/10 23:38:42 pettai Exp $

